## gpios

**Value type:** `<prop-encoded-array>` encoded as a list of phandle + gpio-specifier pairs

A list of GPIO specifiers, one per GPIO consumed by the device. The number of cells in each GPIO specifier is determined by the `#gpio-cells` property of the referenced GPIO controller node.

Used together with `gpio-names` (if named) to identify each GPIO by purpose.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550-qrd.dts */
reg_usb_vbus: regulator-usb-vbus {
    compatible = "regulator-fixed";
    gpios = <&pm8550_gpios 11 GPIO_ACTIVE_HIGH>;
};
```
